high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the small circular table in the corner.
Pick up the candle on the table.
Turn to your left and walk to the big lamp in the corner.
Turn on the lamp and investigate the candle.
anns.task_desc: Investigate a candle using the light of a big lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk around the right side of the table all the way to the far right corner.
Pick up the candle on the table.
Turn left and walk past the TV to the floor lamp in the other corner.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a candle by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: move to the end table on the opposite side of the room on the right
pick up a candle from the table
move to the lamp to the left of the TV
turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Inspect a candle with a lamp.

high_descs: move forward towards the gray chair turn left and move ahead towards the small table with the lamp
take the candle off of the small table
turn to the left and move straight ahead, going around the TV stand towards the tall lamp in the corner
turn on the tall lamp
anns.task_desc: examine the candle by the light of the tall lamp

high_descs: Walk ahead and then to the left behind the couch to the small circular table.
Pick the candle up off the table.
Turn left and walk to the corner of the room which has a lamp in it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a candle illuminated by a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around.  Walk across the room and turn left.  Walk forward until you reach the small, round coffee table with a lamp on it.
Pick up the candle holder with the candle on it.
Turn left.  Walk until you are in between the TV and coffee table.  Look back and forth at the TV and Table 3 times.
Move forward to tall floor lamp slightly ahead on the right.
anns.task_desc: Carry a candle to the floor lamp in the far corner of the living room.
